messageBody:
Hello All,

I just uploaded to the group the Orthodox American English Character
Set to Quikscript Dictionary version 2, in PDF format.

Note that because the file size limitations, the PDF file was Zipped
in a split format. You will need both `QS_Dic ver2_PDF_split.zip' and
`QS_Dic ver2_PDF_split.z01'.

Have both files in the same directory on your computer. Open the
`QS_Dic ver2_PDF_split.zip' file and it will also open the `QS_Dic
ver2_PDF_split.z01' file and create the whole PDF file.

Chuck
